@page "/"
@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager

<h1>Hello, world! Client 1</h1>

<a href="secondapp">Second client</a>
<button @onclick="ToSecondClient">Second client (with forced reload)</button>

<a href="3app">3 client</a>
<button @onclick="To3Client">3 client (with forced reload)</button>

Welcome to your new app.

